Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.05,0:01:21.39,Lyrics Top,,0,0,0,,Mobile Suit Gundam! Gundam!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.05,0:01:21.39,Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Kidou senshi GANDAMU! GANDAMU!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.53,0:01:37.66,Default,,0,0,0,,A half-century has passed\Nsince humanity began moving...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.66,0:01:40.57,Default,,0,0,0,,...its burgeoning population into space.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.20,0:01:43.79,Default,,0,0,0,,These gigantic space cities\Norbiting the Earth...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.79,0:01:46.29,Default,,0,0,0,,...became a second home to humanity...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.29,0:01:50.08,Default,,0,0,0,,...where people were born and raised...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.08,0:01:52.92,Default,,0,0,0,,...and where they died.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.43,0:02:01.51,Default,,0,0,0,,It is the year 0079 of the Universal Century.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.51,0:02:05.64,Default,,0,0,0,,The space city Side 3 proclaimed itself\Nthe Principality of Zeon.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.64,0:02:09.15,Default,,0,0,0,,It launched a war of independence\Nagainst the Earth Federation.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.02,0:02:13.32,Default,,0,0,0,,During this war, the Principality of Zeon\Nand the Federation...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.32,0:02:17.11,Default,,0,0,0,,...caused the deaths\Nof half the total population.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.32,0:02:23.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Humanity was horrified by its own actions.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.75,0:02:35.75,Default,,0,0,0,,The Core Fighter's Escape
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.73,0:02:57.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Ms. Sayla, how are the patients?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.23,0:02:58.78,Default,,0,0,0,,They're doing all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.78,0:03:01.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}- Room 107, situation is stable.\N- Roger.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.95,0:03:05.16,Default,,0,0,0,,All right, ma'am,\Nplease be patient a little longer.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.87,0:03:08.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello! Hello!\NHow are you? How are you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.79,0:03:10.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.04,0:03:12.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello! Hello! Hello...!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.96,0:03:15.96,Default,,0,0,0,,- Hello!\N- Haro, don't cause a ruckus.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.96,0:03:18.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Here you go, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.51,0:03:21.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Fraw Bow, everything's fine here.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.01,0:03:22.38,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.38,0:03:26.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, folks, if you need anything,\Nplease let me know anytime.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.60,0:03:29.73,Default,,0,0,0,,See, this one valve here is shot, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.73,0:03:34.06,Default,,0,0,0,,I see. That's why the output is down 8%.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.06,0:03:37.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Can you calculate it\Nwith a 12% output loss, please?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.52,0:03:38.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Roger!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.28,0:03:44.66,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not going to work.\NWe won't make it to orbit.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.37,0:03:47.45,Default,,0,0,0,,We can connect it to that circuit, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.45,0:03:48.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.75,0:03:55.46,Default,,0,0,0,,- Will the catapult have enough strength?\N- Yes. That should be fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.46,0:03:59.05,Default,,0,0,0,,The central catapult was designed for\Nthe Gunperry. It'll handle a Core Fighter.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.05,0:04:01.13,Default,,0,0,0,,- Thank goodness.\N- But sir...!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.13,0:04:03.13,Default,,0,0,0,,We are soldiers.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.13,0:04:05.09,Default,,0,0,0,,We have a duty to protect civilians.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.09,0:04:07.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, that proves my point.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.10,0:04:10.89,Default,,0,0,0,,If we let these hundred-plus refugees\Noff the White Base...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.89,0:04:13.69,Default,,0,0,0,,...we can return to satellite orbit and...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.69,0:04:17.82,Default,,0,0,0,,This territory is controlled by Zeon.\NThere are children and elderly...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.82,0:04:20.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Are we landing the refugees?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.03,0:04:22.99,Default,,0,0,0,,No, Mr. Bright wants to keep us on the run.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.99,0:04:24.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't say that!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.03,0:04:26.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Was I too harsh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.82,0:04:28.12,Default,,0,0,0,,But you know...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.12,0:04:31.79,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you going to do about food?\NThere're a hundred people who can't fight.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.95,0:04:33.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Kai!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.00,0:04:35.75,Default,,0,0,0,,It's just as the young man says. Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.00,0:04:39.55,Default,,0,0,0,,We were forced to emigrate to space...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.55,0:04:43.26,Default,,0,0,0,,...and we've come back to the Earth\Nwe thought we'd never return to.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.26,0:04:46.89,Default,,0,0,0,,We can't bear to die before\Nwe ever step on the Earth.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.89,0:04:49.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't you all feel that way?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.06,0:04:54.06,Default,,0,0,0,,So, I have an idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.52,0:04:58.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Use the White Base's energy\Nto launch the Core Fighter?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.65,0:05:03.07,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right. With a ballistic trajectory,\Nit'll definitely make it to the target.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.07,0:05:05.49,Default,,0,0,0,,It seems quite possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.49,0:05:07.87,Default,,0,0,0,,You already did the calculations, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.87,0:05:08.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.70,0:05:13.33,Default,,0,0,0,,If we attach the main engine's steam valve\Nto the central catapult, we can do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.33,0:05:15.16,Default,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.79,0:05:20.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Hayato, Fraw Bow...idor B are In an uproar.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.38,0:05:22.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Come right away.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.21,0:05:27.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Nothing will happen as long as\Nwe keep up this stand-off.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.13,0:05:29.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Why not try Amuro's idea?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.51,0:05:32.64,Default,,0,0,0,,There's the question of whether\Nwe can modify the catapult.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.64,0:05:36.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Besides, even if we can do it,\Nwho can withstand the shock of the launch?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.52,0:05:40.52,Default,,0,0,0,,I suggested it. If this plan fails,\Nthere will only be one casualty.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.52,0:05:43.69,Default,,0,0,0,,- Amuro...\N- Well, well. That's some big talk, kid.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.69,0:05:46.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not saying it'll fail.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.32,0:05:49.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Bright. Please approve\Nthe catapult modification.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.53,0:05:50.91,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.91,0:05:52.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Is this all right, Lt. Reed?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.99,0:05:57.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Permission granted.\NIt's vital that we contact General HQ.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.13,0:06:07.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Is all the Gundam data loaded already?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.97,0:06:11.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, sir. All of the data\Nthat we were able to estimate.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.10,0:06:12.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Amazing.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.68,0:06:15.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Based on the data we could\Nobserve from the outside...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.81,0:06:19.19,Default,,0,0,0,,...its performance is far beyond that\Nof our Zaku mobile suits.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.19,0:06:22.36,Default,,0,0,0,,If only we knew more about\Nits internal workings...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.36,0:06:24.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Char. With that mobile suit as your foe...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.98,0:06:27.32,Default,,0,0,0,,...you did well to pursue it for two whole days.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.86,0:06:31.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Garma. Believe me,\Nit was tougher than you think.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.03,0:06:32.57,Default,,0,0,0,,I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.57,0:06:35.95,Default,,0,0,0,,- We shouldn't waste any more time.\N- Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.12,0:06:38.16,Default,,0,0,0,,You're sure you can finish it in 15 minutes?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.58,0:06:43.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Yes. All we have to do Is attachine.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.09,0:06:47.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Get to it, Amuro.\NEat something first. But make it light.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.88,0:06:49.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. I am.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.51,0:06:50.97,Default,,0,0,0,,- All right, listen...\N- Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.97,0:06:52.85,Default,,0,0,0,,The first 30 seconds will be toughest.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.85,0:06:56.35,Default,,0,0,0,,It's awful! The refugees have started a riot!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.60,0:06:58.64,Default,,0,0,0,,- A riot?\N- Why would they...?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.64,0:07:02.10,Default,,0,0,0,,The old folks have taken Katz,\NLetz, and Kikka hostage...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.10,0:07:04.65,Default,,0,0,0,,...and demand that the White Base land!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.48,0:07:07.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't eat anymore, or you'll be sick.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.86,0:07:09.11,Default,,0,0,0,,- Yes, sir.\N- Next...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.65,0:07:13.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Furthermore, Fraw Bow felt sorry\Nfor Katz, Letz, and Kikka...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.78,0:07:15.99,Default,,0,0,0,,...and offered herself as a hostage as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.99,0:07:19.20,Default,,0,0,0,,How many hours have you logged\Non a Core Fighter?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.20,0:07:20.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.29,0:07:22.71,Default,,0,0,0,,18 hours in simulation...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.71,0:07:25.04,Default,,0,0,0,,35 hours in training, and 2 hours in combat.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.04,0:07:29.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Combat, with so little training?\NI guess that's just how it is these days.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.30,0:07:31.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Just gather up your courage and do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.34,0:07:33.39,Default,,0,0,0,,- Yes, sir.\N- Aren't you worried?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.39,0:07:34.43,Default,,0,0,0,,About what?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.43,0:07:37.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Your best friend Fraw Bow is a hostage.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.85,0:07:39.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Show some concern.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.18,0:07:44.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Hayato. Mr. Bright, Ms. Mirai,\NMs. Sayla, and Mr. Ryu are here.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.27,0:07:48.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I trust them to take care of\Nthe White Base's problems.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.19,0:07:51.57,Default,,0,0,0,,I just have to do what I can.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.28,0:07:54.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Amuro's right, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.24,0:07:56.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm off to the central hangar.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.74,0:07:57.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Good luck.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.74,0:08:02.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! You better be ready for enemy fire\Nwhen you leave the White Base.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.67,0:08:06.00,Default,,0,0,0,,You...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.42,0:08:08.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Just who the hell do you think you are?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.84,0:08:10.96,Default,,0,0,0,,No need to get so serious.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.96,0:08:13.01,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm just warning you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.01,0:08:14.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Kai!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.18,0:08:16.35,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right. I'm just a coward.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.35,0:08:19.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Not somebody worth getting upset about.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.56,0:08:21.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that so.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.68,0:08:23.85,Default,,0,0,0,,You're an adult, aren't you, Mr. Kai?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.85,0:08:26.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Then stop being so unpleasant to people!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.04,0:08:44.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Captain, the Trojan Horse is on the move.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.37,0:08:46.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I believe it's on an ascending course!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.21,0:08:47.83,Default,,0,0,0,,- Inform the base.\N- Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.29,0:08:51.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Captain Garma. We have Information{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.42,0:08:53.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The Trojan Horsethe move.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.42,0:08:54.47,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.47,0:08:57.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}- Can you send me the data?\N- Yes, sir. Sending now.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.05,0:08:59.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Estimated data based on laser measurements.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.68,0:09:01.47,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you think, Char?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.47,0:09:04.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Are they trying for an orbital escape?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.43,0:09:06.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Not fast enough for that.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.81,0:09:08.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Or maybe...!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.90,0:09:12.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Get Dren for me!\NPrepare the Komusai for launch!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.73,0:09:14.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Char! What's this about?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.40,0:09:18.95,Default,,0,0,0,,They're cut off from the Federation Forces,\Nand trying to do something about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.41,0:09:21.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Beginning countdown.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.20,0:09:22.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}All right, Amuro?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.87,0:09:24.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}10...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.66,0:09:26.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}8... 7...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.83,0:09:29.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}6... 5... 4...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.92,0:09:32.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}3... 2... 1...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.59,0:09:33.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}0... !{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.02,0:09:52.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Core Fighter on ballistic trajectory.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.11,0:09:54.15,Default,,0,0,0,,The Trojan Horse launched something!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.15,0:09:56.07,Default,,0,0,0,,- Is it on a ballistic trajectory?\N- Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.24,0:10:00.03,Default,,0,0,0,,They're trying to shoot over us\Nand make contact with Federation HQ.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.03,0:10:03.87,Default,,0,0,0,,The radar's no use above the base\Nbecause of the Minovsky particles.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.87,0:10:07.54,Default,,0,0,0,,- What should we do, Char?\N- We pursue! Can we intercept it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.54,0:10:10.71,Default,,0,0,0,,We can launch in a minute,\Nand intercept in 2 minutes 50 seconds!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.71,0:10:12.42,Default,,0,0,0,,- All right!\N- Char!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.42,0:10:15.17,Default,,0,0,0,,He hasn't changed at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.17,0:10:17.34,Default,,0,0,0,,All right. Contact the Gaw attack carrier.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.34,0:10:19.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Tell them to cover Char!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.86,0:10:35.15,Default,,0,0,0,,I gave a rough explanation\Nof our situation. But...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.15,0:10:38.07,Default,,0,0,0,,We don't want to hurt anybody here.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.07,0:10:40.49,Default,,0,0,0,,We just want to hear the truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.49,0:10:43.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Then you shouldn't need to take hostages.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.87,0:10:52.46,Default,,0,0,0,,- Everyone, holster your sidearms.\N- What?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.46,0:10:54.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Put them away!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.09,0:11:00.22,Default,,0,0,0,,My dear grandson\Nis supposed to be on Earth.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.22,0:11:04.93,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to see my home town one more time,\Nand the river nearby.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.93,0:11:08.81,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to see the husband\NI was separated from.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.81,0:11:11.90,Default,,0,0,0,,I never said we weren't\Ngoing to land on Earth.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.10,0:11:14.94,Default,,0,0,0,,How long until we can land?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.94,0:11:17.57,Default,,0,0,0,,I want you to tell me exactly when it will be.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.99,0:11:21.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I feel bad that you have to deal with this...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.82,0:11:25.62,Default,,0,0,0,,...but in order to talk directly to you\Nas equals, in a war situation...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.62,0:11:28.41,Default,,0,0,0,,...it was necessary to take these children.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.37,0:11:31.92,Default,,0,0,0,,We are doing the best we can.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.92,0:11:34.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Bright, please come right away!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.09,0:11:39.21,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.21,0:11:41.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Please come quickly! Quickly!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.30,0:11:44.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Amuro, we should have radio contact now!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.89,0:11:47.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Amuro! This is the White Base!\NPlease respond!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.72,0:11:51.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Please respond! Core Fighter? Amuro?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.31,0:11:54.35,Default,,0,0,0,,- Maybe he was shot down.\N- Don't joke around!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.35,0:11:56.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Enemy approaching!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.11,0:11:58.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Enemy craft pursuing Core Fighter!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.28,0:11:59.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Contact in 1 minute!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.82,0:12:02.20,Default,,0,0,0,,- Is it Char?!\N- l-It can't be...!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.20,0:12:04.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Amuro! Amuro! Please respond!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.78,0:12:08.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Amuro! Answer me! Amuro!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.74,0:12:12.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Amuro! This is the White Base!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.37,0:12:21.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Mobile Suit Gundam
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.38,0:12:28.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Mobile Suit Gundam
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.53,0:12:43.49,Default,,0,0,0,,- How much longer?\N- We should see it in 30 seconds.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.49,0:12:45.74,Default,,0,0,0,,- Amuro!\N- Has the enemy spotted him?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.74,0:12:48.45,Default,,0,0,0,,- There's no answer!\N- Give Amuro some cover!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.53,0:12:51.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Missiles checked! Ready anytime!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.79,0:12:53.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Mirai, full speed ahead!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.96,0:12:57.00,Default,,0,0,0,,He's going to have to lower\Nthe Core Fighter's course.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.00,0:12:58.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Roger.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.00,0:13:01.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Main engine, I need the maximum output\Nat our current state.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.59,0:13:03.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Can't we use the radar?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.17,0:13:05.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Only at 30% accuracy.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.38,0:13:08.47,Default,,0,0,0,,The Minovsky particles are too dense\Nconsidering we're on Earth.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.64,0:13:12.31,Default,,0,0,0,,I can make it out. You want to try it, Bright?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.31,0:13:14.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Fire! It'll be a diversion!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.64,0:13:16.60,Default,,0,0,0,,All right! Launch!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.19,0:13:18.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Missiles!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.15,0:13:22.82,Default,,0,0,0,,The Trojan Horse is just firing at random.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.82,0:13:26.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Move in on the enemy fighter!\NThose missiles won't hit us.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.32,0:13:27.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.91,0:13:32.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Amuro! Wake up! Amuro!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.50,0:13:35.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Amuro! Amuro!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.58,0:13:39.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Please respond! Amuro!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.33,0:13:40.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Where...?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.59,0:13:42.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Are you awake, Amuro?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.46,0:13:44.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Ms. Sayla...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.05,0:13:47.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}There's an enemy Interceptor nearby.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.43,0:13:54.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Calm down! Calm down!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.39,0:13:59.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Dren, these vulcan gun sights\Naren't properly aligned!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.31,0:14:03.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Amuro, you mustn't get shot down!\NListen... Watch the enemy carefully.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.53,0:14:07.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Watch carefully.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.32,0:14:09.32,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right...!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.32,0:14:13.45,Default,,0,0,0,,That craft is merely\Nan atmospheric re-entry capsule.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.45,0:14:15.45,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not a fighter!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.55,0:14:29.51,Default,,0,0,0,,You're finished, Char!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.35,0:14:35.89,Default,,0,0,0,,- That's a direct hit!\N- Don't worry. The damage isn't fatal.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.89,0:14:37.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Go into a dive!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.90,0:14:46.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Can't the White Base\Ngive me better support?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.78,0:14:48.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Why can't we launch those missiles?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.95,0:14:52.03,Default,,0,0,0,,The Dopps are positioned\Nbetween us and the Core Fighter.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.03,0:14:55.37,Default,,0,0,0,,If we fire missiles, there's the possibility\Nthat we could hit the Core Fighter!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.37,0:14:56.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Friendly fire, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.50,0:15:04.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Bright! I don't have a chance\Nagainst six fighters!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.92,0:15:07.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Bring Amuro back to the White Base.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.30,0:15:09.13,Default,,0,0,0,,All hands! Prepare for anti-air combat!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.13,0:15:12.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Amuro, return to ship. Nice and steady.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.34,0:15:14.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Hug the land contours as best you can.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.55,0:15:15.18,Default,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.39,0:15:17.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Bright and Lt. Reed are ordering it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.93,0:15:21.94,Default,,0,0,0,,- He bit off more than he could chew.\N- Why, you...!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.94,0:15:24.77,Default,,0,0,0,,What's your problem? What did I do?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.57,0:15:30.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Take that attitude again\Nand I'll throw you out! Even into space!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.86,0:15:32.61,Default,,0,0,0,,I got it, Mr. Bright.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.61,0:15:34.24,Default,,0,0,0,,The Core Fighter is returning!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.83,0:15:38.50,Default,,0,0,0,,He seems to have given up.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.50,0:15:41.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Dopp team, don't lose him!\NDren, can we give chase?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.58,0:15:44.58,Default,,0,0,0,,- Yes, sir. We'll be fine for a while.\N- All right, go!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.22,0:15:58.85,Default,,0,0,0,,The Gaw attack carrier is ascending.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.85,0:16:00.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Have them launch more Dopps.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.60,0:16:02.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to end this in the air.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.56,0:16:03.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.28,0:16:12.61,Default,,0,0,0,,I got away! There's the White Base!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.45,0:16:18.41,Default,,0,0,0,,The Core Fighter has entered firing range.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.41,0:16:22.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Bring it in while setting up a defense net.\NTransfer to the Gundam ASAP!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.91,0:16:24.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Amuro, do you read?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.58,0:16:27.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you think you can fight\Nan aerial battle in the Gundam?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.84,0:16:29.38,Default,,0,0,0,,An aerial battle?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.38,0:16:32.22,Default,,0,0,0,,But the Gundam is\Na ground combat weapon!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.22,0:16:36.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Don't worry. You can safely spend{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.18,0:16:37.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}You can do It!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.85,0:16:39.47,Default,,0,0,0,,You're asking too much!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.47,0:16:41.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't have those kinds of skills!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.56,0:16:44.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't you want to live through this, Amuro?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.02,0:16:46.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Hurry back to the White Base.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.11,0:16:49.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, come on...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.74,0:16:53.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Begin firing!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.87,0:17:07.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Lower the Core Fighter landing hook!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.47,0:17:16.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Landing alignment is OK. I'm coming in.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.49,0:17:39.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Control conversion, complete!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.62,0:17:43.37,Default,,0,0,0,,But Ms. Sayla... I don't know if...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.37,0:17:46.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Amuro, no one's doing any of this{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.87,0:17:49.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}But Amuro, you have real talent.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.79,0:17:51.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Believe In yourself.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.54,0:17:53.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The hatch will open now.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.81,0:18:07.98,Default,,0,0,0,,A mobile suit!\NEnemy mobile suit has emerged!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.98,0:18:12.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll fight in my Zaku!\NMove the Komusai above the enemy!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.44,0:18:13.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.53,0:18:21.78,Default,,0,0,0,,- A Zaku is descending! It's Char!\N- What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.78,0:18:23.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Char!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.95,0:18:27.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Here I go!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.04,0:18:32.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I've got 1 minute 20 seconds\Nbefore I hit the ground.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.17,0:18:34.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Can I beat him before then?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.72,0:18:43.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn you!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.89,0:18:48.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Where's Char?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.74,0:19:01.16,Default,,0,0,0,,What they call freefall on Earth...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.16,0:19:03.37,Default,,0,0,0,,...isn't as "free" as the phrase suggests.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.79,0:19:08.20,Default,,0,0,0,,The Gundam is in the way!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.20,0:19:10.37,Default,,0,0,0,,H-Hey! What are you people doing...?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.37,0:19:13.54,Default,,0,0,0,,N-Now, wait a minute...!\NThis is the...!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.54,0:19:15.38,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.38,0:19:16.63,Default,,0,0,0,,You people are...!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.63,0:19:19.05,Default,,0,0,0,,So, it seems like we can't land after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.05,0:19:22.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Please get me on to the Earth.\NI'm begging you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.30,0:19:23.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.76,0:19:26.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Please return to your rooms,\Nand don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.72,0:19:28.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Please, quickly...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.02,0:19:31.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, what are you doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.73,0:19:33.86,Default,,0,0,0,,We will not move an inch.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.86,0:19:36.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Not until we land on Earth.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.62,0:19:48.66,Default,,0,0,0,,I used the beams too much!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.21,0:19:55.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}No, Amuro! You must retreat!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.50,0:19:59.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The armor may not hold upspot!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.71,0:20:00.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Y-You're kidding!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.22,0:20:03.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}We'll give you missile cover. Get out!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.05,0:20:05.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Please, don't get hit!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.64,0:20:08.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Roger!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.12,0:20:34.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}- Damn Trojan Horse!\N- Char, can you hear me?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.58,0:20:35.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, Garma.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.63,0:20:37.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The Federation mobile suit.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.34,0:20:42.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}We're going to have toy to fight it.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.34,0:20:43.51,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.72,0:20:47.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}We can only guesster data.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.30,0:20:51.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}But the enemy mobile suit appears to bee...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.06,0:20:53.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}...changing type according to the situation.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.64,0:20:54.98,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.27,0:20:58.65,Default,,0,0,0,,You mean, what I've been seeing...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.65,0:21:02.24,Default,,0,0,0,,...is just one part\Nof the mobile suit's capabilities?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.65,0:21:04.07,Default,,0,0,0,,And yet...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.07,0:21:07.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Well then...!\NHow should we fight it, Garma?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.87,0:21:10.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Return to base. Let's figure It out.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.58,0:21:15.16,Default,,0,0,0,,R-Roger.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.92,0:21:24.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't mind them, Amuro.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.17,0:21:26.34,Default,,0,0,0,,You did well, Amuro.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.34,0:21:28.93,Default,,0,0,0,,- Would you like some tea?\N- Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.93,0:21:33.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I know you, well, all of you...\Nhave been fighting very hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.56,0:21:36.06,Default,,0,0,0,,We understand how difficult it must be.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.06,0:21:40.23,Default,,0,0,0,,We're not saying this\Njust because we're old and difficult...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.23,0:21:42.90,Default,,0,0,0,,We just want to walk on the Earth.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.90,0:21:43.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.86,0:21:45.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Please let us get off the ship here.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.90,0:21:49.16,Default,,0,0,0,,We're just a stone's throw away\Nfrom Federation territory.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.16,0:21:51.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Why can't you wait until then?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.41,0:21:54.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Who's going to guarantee\Nour safety until then?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.00,0:21:57.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I want my son to live. Please save my son!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.79,0:22:01.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Why can't you just find us a safe place\Nand drop us off?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.88,0:22:05.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Can't you people think of anything\Nother than yourselves?!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.17,0:22:07.47,Default,,0,0,0,,How could a child know how the old feel?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.47,0:22:11.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Who would ever fight\Nonly for themselves?!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.22,0:22:14.43,Default,,0,0,0,,We're fighting for all of you people!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.43,0:22:16.81,Default,,0,0,0,,You people make me want to quit!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.81,0:22:18.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Amuro!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.06,0:22:20.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Your tea is ready.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.86,0:22:25.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Please return Fraw Bow\Nand the kids to the bridge.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.74,0:22:29.11,Default,,0,0,0,,We're counting on you, young lady.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.04,0:22:38.66,Default,,0,0,0,,- Amuro!\N- Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.66,0:22:41.17,Default,,0,0,0,,- Were you injured?\N- I'm fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.96,0:22:44.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Can we fly over it?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.00,0:22:46.05,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll have to use the mountains as a shield...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.05,0:22:47.97,Default,,0,0,0,,...and head for the sea.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.97,0:22:49.93,Default,,0,0,0,,I suppose so.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.29,0:23:23.29,Default,,0,0,0,,In order to drop off the refugees,\Na ceasefire is declared.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.29,0:23:27.63,Default,,0,0,0,,However, plans are put into place\Nfor the next round of fighting.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.63,0:23:32.05,Default,,0,0,0,,What will the mother and child\Nwitness on the Earth?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.64,0:23:34.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Mobile Suit Gundam. Next episode...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.89,0:23:36.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Winds of War.
